title: Rhythm Stick - DJ Service - Volume 1 (1989)
description:
Whoa!  Did you think I was done with the classic DJ sets?  Hell NO!

Let&#039;s go back to 1989 when DJ services were off to a great start and remixing music into dance hits was key to making a song even more of a hit...

This DJ service didn&#039;t last long... started in 1989 and closed in 1993.  But - worthwhile listening from some great artists!

I have another one in my computer somewhere - I will post another time.  In the meantime - dance!

Playlist:

1. Good Vibrations - Marky Mark
2. Finally - Cece Peniston
3. Sweet Dreams - Eurythmics
4. Everybody&#039;s Free - Rozalla
5. True - Spandau Ballet
6. Too Blind To See It - Kym Syms
7. Bass Power - Raze
8. The Wave of the Future - Quadrophenia
9. We Gonna Get - RAF
10. Was It Worth It - Pet Shop Boys
11. The Tequila Party - Latino Party
